{"tid":2358260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"六國破滅","createTime":"2021-01-08T04:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T04:19:22.000Z","uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcf6fe2e9483e801470f264fe4e68bc6ba9b7d7","tid":2358260,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"六國破滅，非兵不利，戰不善，弊在賂秦。賂秦而力虧，破滅之道也。<br />\n或曰：「六國互喪，率賂秦耶？」曰：「不賂者以賂者喪。」蓋失強援，不<br />\n能獨完，故曰「弊在賂秦」也。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}